cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision tasks such as 3D shape retrieval and pose estimation from monocular images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves learning an embedding space and training a CNN, which falls under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper deals with robotics-related tasks such as pose estimation, which falls under the sub-category of cs.RO (Robotics). Finally, the paper involves 3D shape retrieval, which can be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics).
